{"tid":1656411,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"（緊急）白色恐怖正在迅速蔓延","createTime":"2019-10-15T14:40:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T17:04:48.000Z","uid":304769,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"670436b434754b10f87fbe0859bb8c59c2d68785","tid":1656411,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T14:40:20.000Z","msg":"中國經過兩天的抵制MBA，他們的策略已經改變，變成用對付香港的兩個舊招，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>分化同白色恐怖來對待美國人</strong></span>（騰訊決定MBA復播，唯獨不播火箭隊），<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有危便有機</span></strong>。這就是我們<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>打國際戰線的一個完美突破口</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n我們要做的事，就是<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>煲大呢件事</strong></span>，帶出<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">今日香港明日世界</span></strong>呢個我們一直想輸出卻無人認真關注的概念，畢竟<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>外國人親身經歷比我地將講一百句都有用</strong></span>。<br />\n各位國際戰線的手足們，我希望我們能更清楚具體的向外國人表達今日香港明日世界。例如我們應該指出：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n1.他們如果不發聲反對赤納粹，明天將會被白色恐怖禁聲。<br />\n2.今天不杯葛為錢舔共的企業，明天將會被中共支配他們的工作，經濟，起居，娛樂。<br />\n3.全世界的自由已經危在旦夕，不站起來對抗中共，明天將會全世界為之所操控和奴役。<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n麻煩大家幫推到國際戰線手足睇到"},{"pid":"01244c1c98e4a57660850c3fa6c38d659ca0aba8","tid":1656411,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T14:43:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bHH8FUF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbHH8FUF.jpg&h=3fd66e79&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"2d7daa13998b168e27d50c0665f2e9407e219c08","tid":1656411,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T15:35:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkg